 for this day" border=0 src="includes/anchor.gif" ></a> <b>Tuesday, February 6,
2001</b>

<p><b><a
 
      href="http://www.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl?ACCT=104&amp;STORY=/www/story/02-06-2001/0001420929&amp;EDATE=" 
     >I/NET
Opens Chicago Office To Develop Conversational Interface
Technology</a>.</b> This is us, of course.

<p><a
 
      href="http://www.prnewswire.com/cgi-bin/stories.pl?ACCT=104&amp;STORY=/www/story/02-06-2001/0001420807&amp;EDATE=" 
